metadata.title: Marbled Murrelets Boat Based Telemetry
metadata.description: Data Type: Birds;  Boat based telemetry relocations for 47 radio tagged marbled murrelets tracked during July and August 1994 field season. Database Record of boat survey observations. Data intended for research and management purposes.
